OL,3,CTheatre boss 'won't lose faith' as
OL,4,Crefurbishment works to take another
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports correspondent Andy
OL,8,FBonner has the latest developments on
OL,9,Fthe Oldham Coliseum refurbishment.
OL,11,FThe boss of an historic theatre which
OL,12,Fwas rescued by the people of its town
OL,13,Fhas promised she won't lose faith if
OL,14,Fthe reopening is pushed further back.
