OL,3,CTheatre boss 'won't lose faith' as
OL,4,Crefurbishment works to take another
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FMulti-million pound renovations at
OL,8,FOldham Coliseum, Greater Manchester,
OL,9,Fwere expected to be completed in time
OL,10,Ffor the 2025 pantomime season but
OL,11,Funexpected issues found in the aging
OL,12,Fbuilding mean that it is unlikely to
OL,13,Fopen its doors again for at least
OL,14,Fanother 12 months.
OL,16,FMartina Murphy, who was brought in as
OL,17,FChief Executive Officer earlier this
OL,18,Fyear, said: "Renovations of old
OL,19,Fbuildings have a habit of revealing
OL,20,Fthemselves in really unhelpful ways.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
