OL,3,CTheatre boss 'won't lose faith' as
OL,4,Crefurbishment works to take another
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,F"At the moment we're still set to open
OL,8,Fat the end of next year (but) you
OL,9,Fcan't tell.
OL,11,F"We're still hoping it will be
OL,12,Fpantomime next year but if it's not
OL,13,Fwe'll move with that and adapt because
OL,14,Fthat's what we do."
OL,16,FMurphy, who described herself as a
OL,17,F"working class kid" from Oldham, has
OL,18,Fcome full circle with her role
OL,19,Fbringing her back to the place where
OL,20,Fshe saw her first pantomime.
