OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FThe "magic and energy" of the theatre
OL,8,Fwas the reason she developed an
OL,9,Finterest in the arts, she added.
OL,11,F"If you talk to people, it's the very
OL,12,Ffabric of their life. It's the place
OL,13,Fthey met their wife for the first
OL,14,Ftime. It's their first pantomime."
OL,16,FNow as CEO, she has taken on a
OL,17,Fsignificant challenge which she
OL,18,Fbelieves she can accomplish thanks to
OL,19,Fher Oldham roots.
