OL,3,CTheatre boss 'won't lose faith' as
OL,4,Crefurbishment works to take another
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,F"It's a grit, the humour, the
OL,8,Fresilience. When everybody else stops
OL,9,Fyou just keep going, one foot in front
OL,10,Fof the other."
OL,12,FThe theatre, which originally opened
OL,13,Fin 1887, closed in March 2023 after
OL,14,Flosing Arts Council funding.
OL,16,FThe community rallied together in a
OL,17,Fcampaign spearheaded by celebrities
OL,18,Fsuch as Mr Bates vs the Post Office's
OL,19,FJulie Hesmondhalgh.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
