OL,4,Crefurbishment works to take another
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FIn 2024, Oldham Council agreed to foot
OL,8,Fthe bill for a #10m refurbishment to
OL,9,Fbring the building back into use.
OL,11,FHowever, builders found it "in a state
OL,12,Fof dilapidation due to water ingress
OL,13,Fand an asbestos strip" leading to more
OL,14,Fmoney being re-allocated to the
OL,15,Fproject.
