OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FThe project is part of a wider
OL,8,Fregeneration of the town centre and
OL,9,Ftheatre bosses are exploring the idea
OL,10,Fof a cultural campus that would move
OL,11,Fback-of-house operations into the
OL,12,Fvisibility of the high street.
OL,14,F"If it is the people's theatre, then
OL,15,Flet it be the people's theatre. Let
OL,16,Fthe people be able to see and get
OL,17,Finvolved in every aspect of it," said
OL,18,FMurphy.
