OL,7,FThe council even plans to spend #1m
OL,8,Fbuying and demolishing a vacant
OL,9,Fbuilding in the town centre to improve
OL,10,Fthe sight-lines to the Coliseum.
OL,12,FIt hopes to replace Harry's Bar with
OL,13,Fan "attractive town square" that will
OL,14,Fhelp entice people towards the theatre
OL,15,Fand shops.
