OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FIn drawing up its plans and to avoid
OL,8,Fhistory repeating itself, the
OL,9,Forganisation is looking at how the
OL,10,Ftheatre failed.
OL,12,FMartina Murphy is keen to highlight
OL,13,Fits heritage and people's emotional
OL,14,Fconnection to the place but she says
OL,15,Fthe town must be "brave and bold" to
OL,16,Flook forward with "huge ambitions for
OL,17,Fthe next generation."
OL,19,FIndeed, the Coliseum has taken the
OL,20,Ftheatre into the community while the
OL,21,Fbuilding has been closed.
