OL,4,Crefurbishment works to take another
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FThey've set the scene in a library,
OL,8,Fchapel, shopping centres, parks,
OL,9,Fmoorlands and meadows, casting their
OL,10,Fnet far and wide to encourage people
OL,11,Fto engage.
OL,13,FMurphy said the Coliseum project is a
OL,14,F"risk worth taking".
OL,16,F"I want it to be the real people's
OL,17,Ftheatre. I want everyone to feel that
OL,18,Fthey can come in not just when a show
OL,19,Fis on stage but whenever they want.
