OL,3,CTheatre boss 'won't lose faith' as
OL,4,Crefurbishment works to take another
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,F"I want them to see themselves in
OL,8,Fevery fabric... I want them to see
OL,9,Fthemselves so they then can be the
OL,10,Fbeacons of this town, go out and do
OL,11,Fsomething really exciting.
OL,13,F"Sometimes you've just got to watch
OL,14,Fpeople be incredible so you can be
OL,15,Fincredible too."
